      },
      "date": "2019-06-20 22:01:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI see. Thank you, Chris. I'll keep eyes on the fix for the ip2nets parsing. After it lands, I'll back-port right away and make the patch series ready for landing to b2_12.",
